				\begin{document}$$Fd\bar{3}m,$$\end{document}Fd3¯m, and cycling degradation mechanism of undesired reactions between LNMO and electrolyte.

As a promising cathode candidate for application in HVLIBs, LNMO has its own special crystal structure. It has two kinds of spinel crystal structures, face-centered cubic (FCC, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
